Global mineral constraints on dust shortwave radiative effects
                    Longlei Li 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0003-2107-84591, Natalie M. Mahowald 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-2873-997X1, Ron L. Miller 
